sections.heading: to 74-4D-8 - Repealed.
sections.text: Repeals.— Laws 1990, ch. 124, § 23 repealed 74-4D-1 to 74-4D-8, as enacted by Laws 1988, ch. 70, §§ 1 to 7 and 12, and as amended by Laws 1989, ch. 324, § 38, and Laws 1989, ch. 305, §§ 1 and 2, relating to petroleum storage cleanup, effective July 1, 1990. For provisions of former sections,seethe 1989 NMSA 1978 onNMOneSource.com.
